People do all kinds of things, they think others wont mind just because they dont.  Which is why so many value their privacy, they know how much information is out there and are comfortable with it.<br>
<br>
Someone said they didnt care as long as there wasnt a camera in their shower, well thats just where YOU draw the line.  Others wouldnt mind the camera in the shower, and actually put it up on the web themselves.<br>
<br>
Privacy has nothing to do with hiding crimes, its just a matter of what individuals are comfortable with giving out.  Thats why there are US laws about breaking and entering, even &quot;just&quot; electronic breaking and entering.  Which is basically what scanning and reporting your memory or task list would be doing, unless you agree to it.<br>
